Subject: Re: [T2] piston cylinder-to-case gaskets

At 11:23 AM 04/20/2002, you wrote:

>with the gasket set i received 3 sets of gaskets. two sets apear to be
>identical and one set thinner. can folks guide me with which to use as i
>put cylinders on? seems like it was discussed at least a million times, but
>i can't find in library or archives. THANKS!   - steve

You will need to measure the deck heights to determine the correct 
thickness of washers to use. Berg sells the tools and instructions on how 
to do this. Verifying this, and many other specs, is not optional if you 
wish to rule out poor performance or burned pistons and valves. 

